OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDeportation of grandmother 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwith Alzheimer's paused    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Sweden has "placed on hold" the        
OL,6, deportation of a British grandmother   
OL,7, with Alzheimer's, her family have told 
OL,8, the BBC.                               
OL,10,FKathleen Poole, 74, was told to leave  
OL,11,Fthe country after her application to   
OL,12,Fremain post-Brexit was rejected.       
OL,14,FHer family have been told that Swedish 
OL,15,Fauthorities will continue to plan for  
OL,16,Fthe deportation, but have paused any   
OL,17,Forder to carry it out for now.         
OL,19,FMrs Poole's daughter-in-law said: "I   
OL,20,Fjust want an end to this situation".   
